{
  "uid": "gaia-control",
  "title": "gaia — DMA Control-Event Spine",
  "tags": [
    "gaia",
    "control",
    "dma"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### DMA control-event spine\nBoundary events (L2) drain dma-side via `dma_common.boundary_bridge` → `boundary.jsonl` + OTLP→**Loki**. The by-code / by-severity panels count the Loki events (the count-connector→Prometheus path is bypassed: count emits delta, the prom exporter wants cumulative — contrib #30203). Loop-cycle RED is span-derived (`dma_debug_dma_tracing_*`) via `loop_event_bridge`. **L1 effective-drive gauges** (`effective_kp/kd`, `command_age`) need the deferred L5 `dma_main` emission to `/metric_events` — that panel reads *No data* until then."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Boundary events by severity (count/interval)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "queryType": "range",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (severity_text) (count_over_time({service_name=\"dma.control\"} | code != \"\" [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{severity_text}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Boundary events by code (count/interval)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "values": ["lastNotNull"] }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "queryType": "range",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (code) (count_over_time({service_name=\"dma.control\"} | code != \"\" [$__auto]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{code}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Loop-cycle rate (spanmetrics) by span",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by(span_name) (rate(dma_debug_dma_tracing_calls_total[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{span_name}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Loop-cycle p99 latency (spanmetrics)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by(le, span_name) (rate(dma_debug_dma_tracing_duration_seconds_bucket[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99 {{span_name}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "L1 effective drive — awaiting L5 (No data expected)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "dma_debug_command_age_ms",
          "legendFormat": "command_age_ms (pending L5)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Recent boundary events",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 19 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "loki" },
          "expr": "{service_name=\"dma.control\"}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
